# {{lb|en|ornithology}} A group of female birds mated to or associated with a breeding male.
#* {{quote-book|1=en|year=1886|translator=H.L. Br&aelig;kstad|author=Peter Christen Asbj&oslash;rnsen|authorlink=Peter Christen Asbj&oslash;rnsen|title=Folk and Fairy Tales|page=90|passage=In the meantime we were hidden in a close juniper thicket on the little knoll, and expected the capercailzie cock every moment; but our old friend tarried a long time in his '''harem'''.}}
# {{lb|en|slang}} Any significant number of women together as a group; a [[bevy]].
# {{lb|en|uncountable}} A [[genre]] of [[anime]] and [[manga]] in which a man is the [[love interest]] of three or more women.

